<br>
1. From level 1-20 it's easy.<br>
<br>
Just get the char you want to power level. Position him out of the way, and YOU GO PULL SOMETHING. Pull it with atols. When it gets near the lowbie, YOU ROOT IT. Get close to the mob and let it hit you. If you keep rooting it, it wont ever get off of you.<br>
<br>
At higher levels, Quad kite mobs until they are almost dead, Root each mob individually, and then zone. Have your other character finish the 4 mobs off<br>
